{"tid":1587992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 我室友好撚臭","createTime":"2019-09-22T15:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:49:48.000Z","uid":197452,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"147a05ed7051db489f5e8adddd2b7d659c4e1ac0","tid":1587992,"uid":197452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"小弟外國留學緊<br />\n但係同房大陸人好少沖涼<br />\n最高紀錄五日無沖<br />\n一放學就玩手機game<br />\n打撚到訓教<br />\n好撚噪<br />\n名乎其實支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經買咗個香薰頂住<br />\n頭幾日效果幾好<br />\n但之後已經失守<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢陣臭味同陣香味合體咗<br />\n然後進化到好撚臭<br />\n<br />\n佢不停用嗅覺視覺攻擊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求救希望有人救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 佢個頭可以炒至少三碟牛河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b3b7767e5bc7edd67650434e4d36d0fa45ce10","tid":1587992,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"c27bdda0299da5cf3697417e62165b806ce899b4","tid":1587992,"uid":276953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be075e6a0ed10c6f46b9bf0bb58599377a2247a","tid":1587992,"uid":197452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58a602e4a99308307b200caa860973bbbcfeb437","tid":1587992,"uid":289641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:06:17.000Z","